      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-quality 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a factory variable M differential. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feel. An uncompromising example of BMW\u2019s 'Ultimate Driving Machine' at its zenith.",
