      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been preserved with obsessive attention to detail. This car has been kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like factory luster, free from rock chips, swirl marks, or even the slightest door ding. It has recently undergone a professional multi-stage paint correction and has been sealed with a five-year ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains taut with zero bolster wear, the original floor mats are pristine, and the dashboard is entirely free of UV fading or stress cracks. Mechanically, this vehicle is in peak performance condition. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records documenting every fluid flush and inspection since day one. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. All electronics, safety features, and climate control systems function perfectly. The sale includes two original master keys, the factory window sticker, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a showroom-quality example that has been maintained to the highest possible standard.",
